General.Name: Kingfisher Mining Ltd
General.Description: Kingfisher Mining Limited operates as a copper, gold, and base metals exploration company. It holds interest in the Boolaloo, Kingfisher, Mick Well, and Arthur River projects located in the Northwest of Western Australia. Kingfisher Mining Limited was incorporated in 2018 and is based in Perth, Australia.
